Text: Thank you (and for the other two as well).  I do hope Part II is coming?  (and Philosophical Fragments and Stages would also be wonderful).

@epound - Unfortunately, I haven't found copies of the other volumes in the "Kierkegaard's Writings" series and I've uploaded everything I have.  I was also left with that edge-of-your-seat, cliffhanger feeling at the end of Either/Or, Part 1, but what can you do?  Hopefully, more volumes will eventually appear!
